title: New: Rosie Carney – Awake Me
body:
**Rosie Carney’s** debut track released midway through last year proved one of 2016’s most poignant, alluring moments.

Her second offering, _Awake Me_, again showcases her stunning songwriting, building to a magnificent, spellbinding finale. Check it out below.
